author: R. SEKARAN
title: Lorry overturns on Penang Bridge
text:
7:37 PM Lorry overturns on Penang Bridge by r. sekaran Police personnel working to clear the lorry on the Penang Bridge 
GEORGE TOWN: A truck heading towards Perai overtuned on the Penang Bridge creating a three kilometre jam at about 5.30pm on Monday. 
The accident brought traffic to a standstill, with the jam crawling until Sungai Pinang on the island. 
It further compounded the peak hour traffic jam which normally occurs from the bottleneck at Udini Road to the bridge. George Town OCPD Asst Comm Mior Faridalathrash Wahid said the truck was removed at about 7pm and traffic has since returned to normal.
